**Teams:** Backend Team (BACKEND), Security Team (SECURITY)

**Created:** 1/10/2024
**Updated:** 1/25/2024

## Description

Complete overhaul of the authentication system to improve security and user experience.

## Goals
- Implement OAuth 2.0 / OpenID Connect
- Add multi-factor authentication
- Improve password reset flow
- Add social login options

## Technical Requirements
- JWT tokens with proper rotation
- Rate limiting on auth endpoints
- Audit logging for security events
- GDPR compliance for user data

## Latest Update

**By:** Jane Lead
**When:** 1/22/2024
**Health:** onTrack

Great progress this week! The OAuth implementation is nearly complete and we're on track for our Q1 delivery. The team has been collaborating well across backend and security concerns.

**This week's highlights:**
- OAuth 2.0 flow implementation 80% complete
- MFA design reviews completed
- Security penetration testing scheduled

**Next week:**
- Complete OAuth testing
- Begin MFA implementation
- Finalize UI designs

